# Environment Variables Configuration

## Backend (.env)
```bash
# Database Configuration
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=attendance_tracker
DB_USERNAME=attendance_user
DB_PASSWORD=secure_password

# JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here-at-least-256-bits-long
JWT_EXPIRATION_MS=86400000

# Google Maps API
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-api-key-here

# Razorpay Configuration
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your-razorpay-key-id
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your-razorpay-key-secret

# Email Configuration (for password reset, notifications)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password

# WebSocket Configuration
WS_PORT=8081
WS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001

# File Upload Configuration
UPLOAD_PATH=/tmp/uploads
MAX_FILE_SIZE=10MB

# Application Configuration
APP_NAME=Employee Attendance Tracker
APP_URL=http://localhost:8080
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
COMPANY_ADMIN_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Security Configuration
BCRYPT_STRENGTH=12
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001,http://localhost:8081
```

## Frontend (.env.local)
```bash
# API Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=ws://localhost:8081

# Google Maps
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-api-key-here

# Razorpay
NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your-razorpay-key-id

# Application
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=Employee Attendance Tracker
```

## Mobile App (.env)
```bash
# API Configuration
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
WS_URL=ws://localhost:8081

# Google Maps
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-api-key-here

# Application
APP_NAME=Employee Attendance Tracker
```

## PC Agent (.env)
```bash
# API Configuration
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api

# Application
APP_NAME=Employee Attendance Tracker
```